OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late brightness.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fwith variable amounts of cloud. Patchy
OL,9,Ffrost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FMany areas will have a dry
OL,12,Fday with some spells of sunshine, some
OL,13,Fhigh cloud around. Patchy rain
OL,14,Fpossible across western Tayside later.
OL,15,FWarm across the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
