OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fon Wednesday morning, brighter in the
OL,7,Fafternoon, quite warm. Rain on
OL,8,FThursday morning followed by a few
OL,9,Fshowers in the afternoon. Rain likely
OL,10,Fon Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
